### 1. Place Order (Customer)
POST http://localhost:3000/orders/place
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CUSTOMER_JWT_TOKEN

### 2. Get My Orders (Customer)
GET http://localhost:3000/orders/my-orders
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CUSTOMER_JWT_TOKEN

### 3. Get Specific Order (Customer)
GET http://localhost:3000/orders/ORDER_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CUSTOMER_JWT_TOKEN

### 4. Cancel Order (Customer)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/orders/ORDER_ID/cancel
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CUSTOMER_JWT_TOKEN

### 5. Get All Orders (Admin Only)
GET http://localhost:3000/orders
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN

### 6. Update Order Status (Admin Only)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/orders/ORDER_ID/status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "PROCESSING"
}